snippet.title: Forgotten Hill Disillusion - Teaser
snippet.description:
Are you ready to face Forgotten Hill Museum? Can you solve the mystery and escape? But, above all, Can you survive?
All infos at: https://www.forgotten-hill.com/disillusion/

Forgotten Hill Disillusion is coming in Fall 2019, wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1133930/Forgotten_Hill_Disillusion/

Soundtrack: "Evening of Chaos"
Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
